page.title: 09INTERSTING PEOPLE
page.content: {q.4Are the changes for the better? Oh,I don't think so theres not so much activity in the village with out the trains and buses. {q.5What would you like to be changed? I would like to see more houses being built in the village and so there woud be more people to talk to. It's a fine wee village and a very freindly village,but it would be fine to see more people in it. {q.6What is in the future for {Auchnagatt?} As I say it is a small village I can't see anything in the future for Auchnagat I would like to see more houses being built.
